---
title: Beyond Meat® Mac 'n' Cheese with Baby Spinach
description: Who doesn't love a classic mac 'n' cheese?! Gooey, cheesy, melty comfort! We've paired it with Beyond Meat® to add extra deliciousness and a crispy shallot topping for that desirable crunch and flavour.
